<p>This will eventually be the <code>SubscriptionPlan</code> object for the <em>other</em> duration
of the current plan. So if I have the <em>monthly</em> Farmer Brent, this will be set
to the <em>yearly</em> Farmer Brent plan.</p>
<p>To find that plan, open <code>SubscriptionHelper</code> and add a new function called
<code>findPlanForOtherDuration()</code> with a <code>$currentPlanId</code> argument:</p>
