<p>Cool!</p>
<p>In <code>account.html.twig</code>, scroll down to the Upgrade Plan button. Copy that <em>whole</em>
thing. Then, keep scrolling to the "Next Billing at" section. If the user has a
subscription, paste the upgrade button:</p>
