</p>
<p>And now that I've told you it won't work, let's try it out! Refresh the account
page. Then click the new "Bill yearly" link. Ok:</p>
<blockquote><p>You will be charged $792.05 immediately</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Wait, that doesn't seem right. The yearly plan is $990 per year. Then, if you subtract
approximately $99 from that as a credit, it should be something closer to $891.
Something is not quite right.</p>

    
